description:
Ghost Plane



Aired on 06/17/2007, Narrated by Jonathan Aris



On 14 August 2005, Helios Airways Flight 522, a Boeing 737-300, loses radio contact with air traffic controllers, two fighters from the Hellenic Air Force are sent to intercept and investigate and find all but one person on board not moving. A few moments later, the aircraft runs out of fuel and crashes, killing 121 people.
